{"tid":533754,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"模擬醫院遊戲《杏林也瘋狂》今年秋季正式推出續集！！！","createTime":"2018-01-19T06:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T04:01:37.000Z","uid":55851,"like":130,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"54333ed48857dab2458568c9dc1576fe0ba66d5f","tid":533754,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/151011/thumbnail/38809bc5e629ce45fc13bee2e011cd25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F151011%2Fthumbnail%2F38809bc5e629ce45fc13bee2e011cd25.jpg&h=083acc14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位80、90後機迷請注意！曾風靡一時的模擬醫院電玩遊戲《杏林也瘋狂》（Theme Hospital），事隔21年終於推出續集。新一集遊戲將改名為《Two Point Hospital 》，並繼續保留原作各種奇怪病症，例如最經典的大頭症等，而且玩法與首集大同小異，玩家同樣以院長身份營運醫院，不過畫面就由2D改良成更迫真的3D。日前官方推出首段續集預告片，並宣布將於今年秋季正式推出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1140182/xlarge/fa702badcf8985431b2d054cf5d1afb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1140182%2Fxlarge%2Ffa702badcf8985431b2d054cf5d1afb7.jpg&h=27862375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1997年面世的經典電玩遊戲《杏林也瘋狂》，讓玩家模擬營運一間醫院，其間需要替病人治療各式奇難雜症，並要應付投訴、管理愛找麻煩的工作人員等等。要數最深刻的畫面，莫過於大量病人輪住嘔吐，再請清潔工打掃，以及用針刺破大頭症病人等，忙得不可開交。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲的每一關都會有一間空的醫院，讓玩家設計用途、分配房間及儀器等，達至指定的聲望、治癒人數、盈利等等後，便可以「升級」。隨住醫院等級上升，玩家就可以開始利用儀器研發新的醫療方法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1140666/org/9beba6e0cbda410daa793d318a16833f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1140666%2Forg%2F9beba6e0cbda410daa793d318a16833f.gif&h=b67409a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲續集《Two Point Hospital》由首集的製作班底，包括幕後功臣韋伯利（Mark Webley）及卡爾（Gary Carr），聯同新成員組成的新公司「Two Point Studios」打造而成，日前發行商世嘉（SEGA）釋出首段預告片，片中的病人崔佛（Trevor）患上「燈膽頭症」，為其日常生活帶來不便，而「Two Point Hospital」則積極為他治療。<br />\n<br />\n從預告片中，可見遊戲的人物造型、畫面到各種奇怪的病症，續集均保留了原作的特色，畫面則提升至更迫真的3D效果，讓玩家非常有親切感。世嘉歐洲發行副總裁克拉克（John Clark）表示，目前遊戲已登陸STEAM遊戲平台商店，並預計於今年秋季正式推出發售。<br />\n<br />\n（STEAM）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Rs739pbskxA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRs739pbskxA&d=Q26sThRywBPecVqUHaKi6P%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=838b6e05\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Rs739pbskxA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/151011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2F151011&d=Q26sThRywBPecVqUHaKi6P%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=c00e1576\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/151011</a>"},{"pid":"e505b7318d0ae701df54155abef3f2658a214af5","tid":533754,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:20:54.000Z","msg":"diu正"},{"pid":"3b63609c912cc62f2ab56623f0cacd7d453253cf","tid":533754,"uid":45650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e7afc0b0bcf5ab1775d6c20a9433d61249da32","tid":533754,"uid":85819,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d6cf7612b0f6d5ff6501ecb9c265ab271659dd8","tid":533754,"uid":42202,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:25:24.000Z","msg":"但杏林也瘋狂喺EA到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26c229ada0b8306c32ea9539d0d8f57d6930288","tid":533754,"uid":120232,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"久唔久都玩返"},{"pid":"487543a36f71831808e9ba0d5eaa2e0f574ec7b7","tid":533754,"uid":61201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:26:00.000Z","msg":"細個成日玩"},{"pid":"cb2003cb71499264dcb584abcb836c3df7fa96c6","tid":533754,"uid":161711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201